window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With Charity's fate on the line, Devon and his pack must face the perils of the Realm in search of the elusive warrior fae. With no real experience and against some of the most powerful creatures in existence, they are fighting a losing battle.</p> <p>Thankfully, they don't have to do it alone.</p> <p>Knowing what's at stake, Penny and Emery, the magical powerhouses of the mage world, will lend their aid. Even though Emery is outlawed from stepping foot in the Realm, the pair will try to sneak Charity in the backdoor.</p> <p>If they are caught, they'll all be captured or worse. Much worse.</p> <p>But to make it means Devon will be forced to make a difficult decision that will change his and Charity's life forever.</p> <p>Performed by Jeri Marshall, Elena Anderson, Alexander Amado, Eric Messner, Renee Dorian, Robb Moreira, Ian Putnam, Alyssa Keegan, Rayner Gabriel, Amanda Forstrom, Drew Kopas, Kevin Couto, Samantha Cooper, Troy Allan, Julie-Ann Elliott, Michael John Casey, Nora Achrati, James Konicek, Scott McCormick, Nanette Savard, James Lewis, Rose Elizabeth Supan, Mort Shelby, Khaya Fraites, Debi Tinsley, Holly Adams, Nicole Perez, Lamont Ridgell, Ryan Carlo Dalusung, Yasmin Tuazon, and Julie Hoverson.</p>"; 
